                        <h3>Welcome to my new site</h3>

<p>This I think is maybe the fifth version of my class site I've built and by far the easiest to do. Maybe I've learned a bit more about web dev over the years but I think it may have something to do with using a neat CMS called <a href="http://jkwp.itsligo.ie/blog/git">kirby</a>.<br />
As for content, it's all pretty much migrated across. FOOP20X isn't in here yet but other than that, you should find what you're looking for. I'll pad out more work over the summer... ah, summer...</p>
